<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/fair-work-agency> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Fair Work Agency (FWA) is responsible for enforcing workers’ rights. We’re a single point of contact for workers who believe their rights have not been upheld. FWA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade ."@en .
